          { speaker: 'b', speakerName: 'Jamie', en: 'What would you say to someone who is just beginning and already feels discouraged by how slow the process seems?', zh: '那如果是剛開始的人，已經因為進步太慢而沮喪了，你會想先對他說什麼？' },
          { speaker: 'a', speakerName: 'Mira', en: 'I would say: do not confuse gradual progress with absence. The quiet middle is often where "Carrying the Festival Spirit Forward" becomes honest instead of merely impressive.', zh: '我會說，慢不是失敗。很多時候，慢只是代表你終於走進了真正會塑造你的那一段，而不是只有表面的熱情。' }
